# Implementation Plan: Full Stack RAG Integration for Project Sankofa

This plan outlines the technical steps to transform the **Project Sankofa** prototype into a fully functional, end-to-end AI Academic Survival Copilot.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Branding Decision**: We will standardize the app's visual identity on **Sankofa (by Lighthub)** across all UI elements, replacing the conflicting "STUN-FI NOTES" branding.
>
> **Anthropic API Key**: The backend requires an `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` for Claude API requests. You will need to add this key to a local `.env` file.
>
> **Tesseract OCR System Dependency**: Tesseract OCR requires a system installation of the Tesseract binary. If Tesseract is not installed on the system, the document processing engine will log a warning and fallback gracefully to standard PDF text extraction.

